            "text": "74|24|Tara pichata si ka’le, ‘eya purbarae paraa cali aha yadura bahirae ana eko nahaya’"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 74,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "74|25|‘eyato manuharae'i katha’."
        },
        {
            "chapter": 74,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "74|26|Anatipalame ma'i taka chakbarata (jahannamata) praraesa karaama."
